BICHM.description:
The BICHM (bit interleaved coded hybrid modulation) incremental step in 1/128 bits/symbol added to base modulation bits/symbol for the hybrid modes modulation-format. 
                         0: Base modulation format bits/symbol;
                         1: 1/128 bits/symbol added to base modulation format bits/symbol;
                         ...
                         127: 127/128 bits/symbol added to base modulation format bits/symbol

